      <title>黄金开盘大幅下挫，因股价下跌震动投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周伊始，金价经历了一段坎坷的走势，先是大幅下跌，随后由于交易员评估股市抛售和中东紧张局势的影响而转为上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/gold-gets-dragged-into-selloff-as-share-slide-jolts-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 01:07:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球股市暴跌加剧，推动债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，全球股市抛售加剧，人们越来越担心美联储在支持美国经济放缓的政策方面落后于形势，投资者纷纷转向债券避险。日本股市暴跌，因为交易员认为国内利率将进一步上调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/japanese-stocks-tumble-leading-equities-selloff-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>避险情绪加深，亚洲股市出现严峻里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国经济进一步放缓以及中东紧张局势加剧，投资者纷纷避开风险资产，亚洲股市在新的一周伊始大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/korea-s-kospi-index-plunges-takes-losses-from-july-peak-to-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 00:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
